sequenceDiagram
    title 智能检索 Agent Tool Calling 时序图
    autonumber
    actor 用户
    participant 前端
    participant AgentChatController
    participant AgentRuntime as Agent Runtime
    participant IntentParser as Intent Parser
    participant ToolRouter as Tool Router
    participant SearchTool as Structured Search Tool
    participant KnowledgeTool as Knowledge Tool
    participant RealtimeTool as Realtime Tool
    participant Composer as Response Composer

    note over 用户,Composer: 智能检索 Agent Tool Calling 简化流程

    用户->>前端: 输入智能检索问题
    前端->>AgentChatController: POST /api/agent/chat
    AgentChatController->>AgentRuntime: chat(request, authorization)
    AgentRuntime->>IntentParser: parseIntent(messages, sessionContext)
    IntentParser-->>AgentRuntime: parsedIntent
    AgentRuntime->>ToolRouter: routeTools(parsedIntent, normalizedParams)
    ToolRouter-->>AgentRuntime: search -> parallel(knowledge, realtime)

    AgentRuntime->>SearchTool: search_events(params)
    SearchTool-->>AgentRuntime: topN 候选结果

    par 知识补充
        AgentRuntime->>KnowledgeTool: retrieve_knowledge(topEntities, question)
        KnowledgeTool-->>AgentRuntime: 规则与注意事项摘要
    and 实时确认
        AgentRuntime->>RealtimeTool: check_event_availability(topIds, date)
        RealtimeTool-->>AgentRuntime: 当前可预约状态
    end

    AgentRuntime->>Composer: merge(searchResults, knowledge, realtime)
    Composer-->>AgentRuntime: answerText + cards + disclaimers
    AgentRuntime-->>AgentChatController: AgentChatResponse
    AgentChatController-->>前端: Resp.success(data)
    前端-->>用户: 展示推荐结果、实时状态与注意事项
